<div style="text-align: center;">
<h2 id="toc1"><span><span style="text-decoration: underline;">like my stuff?</span></span></h2>
<p>aw shucks, thanks. i'm open for collabs almost all the time, so just hit me up. it helps if you have an idea though, so don't just come up to me asking to write.</p>
<h2 id="toc2"><span><span style="text-decoration: underline;">srs bznz</span></span></h2>
</div>
<br />
in the event something happens to me and i disappear for 5 years or die, i leave all my non-colab articles entrusted to <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/aismallard" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(4598089); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=4598089&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610148995" alt="aismallard" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=4598089)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/aismallard" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(4598089); return false;">aismallard</a></span>, and all my collab articles with the respective co-authors. The only exception to this is <a href="/moon-champion-s-cinco-de-mayo-extravaganza">moon champion's cinco de mayo extravaganza</a>, which would be left to <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/cadavercommander" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3187823); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3187823&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610148995" alt="CadaverCommander" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3187823)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/cadavercommander" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3187823); return false;">CadaverCommander</a></span>.<img src="https://i.imgur.com/UEQWeKN.png" alt="UEQWeKN.png" class="image" /><br />
